I look thru my spell book to see what I could cast that would help and see Cripple. I think why not give it a shot. Pull a MoB and get it ready for kill. This time when Monk engages she does not seem to be getting hit as hard or as much. Pull another and same. Druid only needs to heal once or very rarely twice a fight now.<br>
I have also cast when we have a 61 Warrior with us but it is hard to tell if it makes much difference. His AC is 300 more than the Monk and he has at least twice as many HP.<br>
I think this spell will get more use from me in the future.<br>
